00:16:00.659 --> 00:16:02.361
Teka, Haruka?

00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:11.470
Paano naging ganito ang mga bagay?

00:16:18.777 --> 00:16:20.679
Sorry sa lahat.

00:16:21.914 --> 00:16:25.217
Nagpa-panic ako
na wala akong nangyayari.

00:16:26.518 --> 00:16:30.356
Pero sigurado akong hindi
rin alam ni Hikaru ang gagawin.

00:16:30.956 --> 00:16:34.159
Walang nangyayari? Naiintindihan ko iyon.

00:16:36.795 --> 00:16:39.531
At saka, ano ang layo?

00:16:40.099 --> 00:16:41.300
pasensya na po.

00:16:42.234 --> 00:16:45.838
Ayokong gumawa ng anumang bagay
na maaaring ikagalit ni Hikaru.

00:16:47.006 --> 00:16:48.607
Masigasig ka pa rin gaya ng dati.

00:16:51.810 --> 00:16:55.914
Hindi ba karaniwang masaya ang isang babae,
sa halip na mababa?

00:16:55.981 --> 00:16:57.883
Kung sobrang kahanga-hanga ang boyfriend nila.

00:16:59.184 --> 00:17:00.152
Well,

00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:05.090
Hikaru's my lover but also my best friend.

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:08.994
Gusto kong maging pantay.

00:17:10.029 --> 00:17:11.497
Para magkasama tayo forever.

00:17:12.264 --> 00:17:13.766
Pantay, ha?

00:17:17.336 --> 00:17:18.203
Pero

00:17:19.304 --> 00:17:22.374
bihira lang may nakakaalam
kung ano ang gusto niyang gawin sa simula.

00:17:23.909 --> 00:17:29.748
At si Mio at Hikaru ay nasa ibang antas
dahil sila ay matagumpay dito.

00:17:29.815 --> 00:17:31.050
Ibang level?

00:17:31.116 --> 00:17:32.084
Karaniwan,

00:17:33.385 --> 00:17:35.854
kailangan mong subukan ang ilang bagay
upang malaman iyon.

00:17:38.023 --> 00:17:40.592
Nasa "wala" side din ako.

00:17:43.062 --> 00:17:43.896
Kaya

00:17:45.831 --> 00:17:47.166
Sinusubukan ko ang iba't ibang bagay.

00:17:47.733 --> 00:17:51.303
At hindi ko
rin nililimitahan ang paghahanap ko ng trabaho sa Tokyo.

00:17:52.004 --> 00:17:52.938
talaga?

00:17:57.443 --> 00:17:58.811
Paano naman tayong dalawa

00:17:59.812 --> 00:18:02.381
palawakin ang aming mga abot-tanaw at subukan ang aming makakaya?

00:18:06.852 --> 00:18:08.053
- Oo!
- Magaling.

00:18:09.054 --> 00:18:09.888
Magandang sagot.

00:18:14.426 --> 00:18:17.663
{\an8}Mr. Napaka-cool pa rin ni Kurotaki.

00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:21.366
{\an8}Siya pa rin ang taong hinahangaan ko,
tulad ng dati.

00:18:22.534 --> 00:18:23.769
{\an8}Ngunit…

00:18:23.836 --> 00:18:24.703
{\an8}Maghintay.

00:18:26.205 --> 00:18:27.506
{\an8}Okay lang ako dito.

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:30.409
{\an8}Paano kung guluhin ka ulit ng mga lalaki?

00:18:30.476 --> 00:18:31.343
{\an8}Ihahatid kita.

00:18:31.410 --> 00:18:33.645
{\an8}Hindi, magiging okay lang ako.

00:18:33.712 --> 00:18:35.814
{\an8}Hindi ko nararamdaman ang nararamdaman ko para kay Hikaru.

00:18:37.983 --> 00:18:40.586
{\an8}Yung gusto kong makasama habang buhay

00:18:41.186 --> 00:18:42.521
{\an8}ay Hikaru.

00:18:43.589 --> 00:18:46.425
{\an8}Maraming salamat sa lahat.

00:18:58.871 --> 00:18:59.905
{\an8}Uy, ako ito.

00:18:59.972 --> 00:19:04.877
{\an8}- Ano? Bakit ka--
- Naaalala mo ba yung sinabi mo sa akin minsan?

00:19:05.911 --> 00:19:08.147
{\an8}- Ano?
- Tungkol kay Haruka.

00:19:08.947 --> 00:19:12.184
{\an8}"Pahalagahan mo siya.
Papatayin kita kapag nasaktan mo siya."

00:19:14.453 --> 00:19:15.587
{\an8}Mayaman iyon.

00:19:18.790 --> 00:19:20.492
{\an8}Mabuting kunin mo siya.

00:19:22.161 --> 00:19:23.228
{\an8}O kung hindi

00:19:25.731 --> 00:19:26.832
{\an8}Binabawi ko siya.

00:19:34.640 --> 00:19:36.575
{\an8}Alam mo ba kung bakit nagbibigay ng singsing ang magkasintahan?

00:19:36.642 --> 00:19:38.844
{\an8}Ipagpatuloy mo lang ang pag-iisip tungkol sa akin.

00:19:38.911 --> 00:19:40.145
{\an8}Well, good luck.

00:19:40.212 --> 00:19:42.247
{\an8}Kung hindi ka masaya, nasasaktan din ako.

00:19:44.383 --> 00:19:45.884
{\an8}Nagkaroon ng aksidente.

00:19:45.951 --> 00:19:47.186
{\an8}Hikaru?

00:19:47.252 --> 00:19:48.120
{\an8}Hindi.

00:19:48.187 --> 00:19:49.755
